{{familytree|border=0|||)|-|v|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|v|-|.|}}
{{familytree|border=0|01|02|||||||03|04| 01={{ill|Urakogori Waketakehiko|ja|浦凝別|12=draft}}<br />[Founder of the Enō clan]<br />(Enō region)|02={{ill|Mitomo Waketakehiko|ja|御友別|12=draft}}<br />[Founder of the Kibi clan]|03={{ill|Kamo Waketakehiko|ja|鴨別|12=draft}}<br />[Founder of the Kasa clan]<br />(Namikugi region)|04={{color|#FC4E6B|Anehime}}<br />[Consort of Ōjin Tennō]<br />(Weaving rites)}}
